<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَحْسَبُونَ}</span> ... يَظُنُّونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَجْوَاهُم}</span> ... مَا تَكَلَّمُوا فِيهِ فِيمَا بَيْنَهُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرُسُلُنَا}</span> ... مَلَائِكَتُنَا الكِرَامُ الحَفَظَةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ}</span> ... عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ اللهَ بِهِ؛ مِنَ الصَّاحِبَةِ، وَالوَلَدِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَذَرْهُمْ}</span> ... اتْرُكْهُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَخُوضُوا}</span> ... يَتَكَلَّمُوا بِبَاطِلِهِمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِلَهٌ}</span> ... مَعْبُودٌ بِحَقٍّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَبَارَكَ}</span> ... تَكَاثَرَتْ بَرَكَةُ اللهِ، وَكَثُرَ خَيْرُهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَهِدَ بِالْحَقِّ}</span> ... أَقَرَّ بِتَوْحِيدِ اللهِ، وَنُبُوَّةِ نَبِيِّنَا مُحَمَّدٍ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَنَّى يُؤْفَكُونَ}</span> ... كَيْفَ يَنْصَرِفُونَ عَنْ عِبَادَةِ اللهِ؟!<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقِيلِهِ}</span> ... وَقَوْلِ مُحَمَّدٍ فِي شَكْوَاهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاصْفَحْ}</span> ... أَعْرِضْ عَنْ أَذَاهُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>